    %h4 Online Resources Temporarily Available During COVID-19:

    %p Due to temporary access provided in response to the COVID-19 emergency 40% of our print collections are now available digitally. We suggest starting with a general #{link_to "catalog search", "clio.columbia.edu"}; if you do not find what you need there please proceed to an e-book search from this page.


    %p This page searches:
    %ul
      %li citations and some full text for our growing collection of recently published e-books
      %li a much larger collection of mostly full-text e-books that are out of copyright, e.g. published before 1925 or a U.S. government document


    %p To search other full-text collections of recently published e-books in the humanities and social sciences, try the individual resources listed in the sidebar to the right. These collections have different strengths but are interdisciplinary.
    
